text: Iwona Marcinkiewicz (born 23 May 1975) is an archer from Poland. Marcinkiewicz competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics, 2004 Summer Olympics, and 2008 Summer Olympics.Iwona Dzięcioł-Marcinkiewicz == References == Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Polish archers Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Poland Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw
